WEBVTT

00:00:27.760 --> 00:00:28.920
[Wei]

00:00:44.880 --> 00:00:46.320
It's not too late to regret now.

00:00:46.320 --> 00:00:47.520
Come with me instead.

00:00:48.440 --> 00:00:49.100
Go with you?

00:00:50.280 --> 00:00:50.920
To do what?

00:00:51.880 --> 00:00:54.010
Rob and murder or swindle and plunder?

00:00:54.280 --> 00:00:56.840
Bully the weak or harass women?

00:00:58.880 --> 00:01:00.520
Should I be like you every day,

00:01:00.520 --> 00:01:02.160
doing shady things,

00:01:02.440 --> 00:01:04.040
living like a rat in the gutter,

00:01:04.040 --> 00:01:06.000
despised and hated by everyone?

00:01:06.960 --> 00:01:09.000
I never knew you were such a talker.

00:01:10.960 --> 00:01:13.090
Talked yourself hoarse, haven't you?

00:01:13.320 --> 00:01:13.850
[Li Ling]

00:01:14.840 --> 00:01:16.200
You slept with my woman,

00:01:17.000 --> 00:01:18.720
and you still have the nerve to act righteous.

00:01:18.720 --> 00:01:20.380
Su Changming, let me tell you,

00:01:20.600 --> 00:01:21.720
from today on,

00:01:22.240 --> 00:01:24.520
I have nothing to do with your Guantian Society.

00:01:24.520 --> 00:01:25.580
Whatever you want,

00:01:25.640 --> 00:01:27.560
get it yourself with your own abilities.

00:01:27.560 --> 00:01:29.600
What I want is none of your business.

00:01:30.000 --> 00:01:30.560
Nongyu,

00:01:31.240 --> 00:01:32.440
don't be fooled by him.

00:01:32.440 --> 00:01:33.500
Only I can help you.

00:01:35.920 --> 00:01:37.520
Li Ling and I appreciate each other

00:01:37.520 --> 00:01:38.380
and are in love.

00:01:39.240 --> 00:01:40.240
This is my choice.

00:01:43.320 --> 00:01:44.000
Fine.

00:01:44.400 --> 00:01:46.160
Since things have come to this,

00:01:47.360 --> 00:01:48.820
I won't be polite anymore.

00:01:49.400 --> 00:01:50.729
Today, between you two,

00:01:51.400 --> 00:01:53.060
only one can leave this place.

00:01:54.520 --> 00:01:55.780
As for who it will be...

00:01:57.360 --> 00:01:58.200
You decide.

00:02:00.400 --> 00:02:02.530
Then I'll give you two choices as well.

00:02:02.680 --> 00:02:04.410
Either kneel and beg for mercy,

00:02:04.680 --> 00:02:05.160
or...

00:02:05.920 --> 00:02:08.180
have your head separated from your body.

00:02:12.800 --> 00:02:13.640
Yu Linxun.

00:02:16.960 --> 00:02:18.220
That sword in his hand,

00:02:18.440 --> 00:02:19.570
is it your father's?

00:02:20.320 --> 00:02:22.720
Indeed, it's my father's treasured sword.

00:02:22.880 --> 00:02:24.880
Then he couldn't possibly know

00:02:25.000 --> 00:02:26.880
who killed your father back then.

00:02:29.000 --> 00:02:30.720
I heard in the army

00:02:31.200 --> 00:02:32.760
that General Feng's treasured sword

00:02:32.760 --> 00:02:35.480
was unfortunately lost during the battle of Tongguan.

00:02:35.480 --> 00:02:36.960
Later when I joined the Chen household,

00:02:36.960 --> 00:02:38.960
I saw Chen Jingbian playing with it.

00:02:39.560 --> 00:02:40.920
If I'm not mistaken,

00:02:41.200 --> 00:02:43.680
you must have bought it from Chen Jingbian.

00:02:43.920 --> 00:02:45.720
So there's no way you could know

00:02:45.760 --> 00:02:47.640
the truth about what happened back then.

00:02:47.640 --> 00:02:48.840
Master Chen, please.

00:02:49.200 --> 00:02:49.640
Come.

00:02:52.920 --> 00:02:53.850
But you used this

00:02:54.200 --> 00:02:55.400
to deceive Yin Niang

00:02:55.760 --> 00:02:56.680
to make her serve him

00:02:56.680 --> 00:02:57.480
and be used by him.

00:02:57.480 --> 00:02:58.280
Am I right?

00:02:59.840 --> 00:03:01.240
Is what he's saying true?

00:03:06.800 --> 00:03:07.400
It is true.

00:03:09.880 --> 00:03:10.480
The sword?

00:03:11.040 --> 00:03:13.280
I did buy it from Chen Jingbian

00:03:13.600 --> 00:03:15.060
and paid quite a sum for it.

00:03:15.760 --> 00:03:16.840
But I wasn't lying.

00:03:17.520 --> 00:03:19.120
Once you get the Firefly Map

00:03:19.480 --> 00:03:20.920
I'll naturally know everything.

00:03:20.920 --> 00:03:23.160
It surely contains records

00:03:23.200 --> 00:03:25.260
about what your father did back then.

00:03:25.520 --> 00:03:26.760
I'll definitely tell you everything.

00:03:26.760 --> 00:03:28.880
Su Changming, you bastard!

00:03:30.200 --> 00:03:31.880
Return the sword to Nongyu.

00:03:32.280 --> 00:03:33.800
I never said I wouldn't return it.

00:03:33.800 --> 00:03:35.600
I offered it to you before,

00:03:36.040 --> 00:03:37.500
but you refused to take it.

00:03:38.400 --> 00:03:38.880
Fine.

00:03:39.120 --> 00:03:40.050
No more arguing.

00:03:42.320 --> 00:03:42.980
Here you go.

00:03:43.079 --> 00:03:43.540
Take it.

00:03:52.600 --> 00:03:53.130
Let's go.

00:03:55.200 --> 00:03:55.680
Wait.

00:03:57.120 --> 00:03:58.600
I've given everything back,

00:03:58.600 --> 00:04:00.400
so at least let me say something.

00:04:00.920 --> 00:04:02.450
I want to make a bet with you.

00:04:02.560 --> 00:04:05.360
Today you're taking both the person and the sword,

00:04:05.600 --> 00:04:06.520
but I dare say

00:04:06.920 --> 00:04:07.960
before long

00:04:09.840 --> 00:04:11.400
you'll bring both the person and the sword

00:04:11.400 --> 00:04:12.530
back to me yourself.

00:04:12.640 --> 00:04:13.500
In your dreams!

00:04:15.280 --> 00:04:17.040
Loser dies.

00:04:17.519 --> 00:04:18.000
Fine.

00:04:19.519 --> 00:04:20.579
I'll take that bet.

00:04:23.440 --> 00:04:23.970
Let's go.

00:04:29.720 --> 00:04:30.520
Young Master,

00:04:30.560 --> 00:04:31.800
are you just letting them leave like this?

00:04:31.800 --> 00:04:32.530
Yes, indeed.

00:04:33.120 --> 00:04:33.850
Don't worry.

00:04:34.920 --> 00:04:36.450
This is just the beginning.

00:04:37.280 --> 00:04:38.540
The best is yet to come.

00:04:48.960 --> 00:04:50.420
Do you want to take a break?

00:04:53.960 --> 00:04:55.440
We're about to enter the city.

00:04:55.440 --> 00:04:57.880
Why don't we go back to Tongxin Quarter first

00:04:57.880 --> 00:05:00.880
and place the jade dagger at General Feng's memorial?

00:05:03.320 --> 00:05:03.920
By the way.

00:05:04.240 --> 00:05:05.960
You mentioned seeing this dagger

00:05:05.960 --> 00:05:07.320
when you were with Chen Jingbian.

00:05:07.320 --> 00:05:09.600
Do you know where this dagger came from?

00:05:11.760 --> 00:05:13.160
I don't know the details.

00:05:13.720 --> 00:05:15.450
I only heard from Yu Yaonou that

00:05:15.760 --> 00:05:17.720
this dagger was probably given

00:05:17.720 --> 00:05:19.380
to Chen Jingbian by An Lushan.

00:05:19.960 --> 00:05:20.490
I believe

00:05:20.920 --> 00:05:23.560
it must have fallen into the hands of the Great Yan army

00:05:23.560 --> 00:05:26.040
after the defeat at Tongguan.

00:05:26.880 --> 00:05:27.960
That old eunuch dog,

00:05:27.960 --> 00:05:28.620
how dare he!

00:05:29.520 --> 00:05:30.280
If I find out

00:05:30.280 --> 00:05:32.080
he had anything to do with what happened,

00:05:32.080 --> 00:05:33.409
I'll tear him to pieces.

00:05:35.159 --> 00:05:35.640
Nongyu.

00:05:37.240 --> 00:05:37.770
Miss Yin.

00:05:38.920 --> 00:05:39.450
I believe

00:05:39.920 --> 00:05:40.650
General Feng

00:05:41.200 --> 00:05:43.000
would never betray his country.

00:05:43.040 --> 00:05:45.200
Someone must have framed him.

00:05:46.000 --> 00:05:46.800
Rest assured,

00:05:47.280 --> 00:05:48.880
I will find the real culprit.

00:05:48.960 --> 00:05:50.080
I will clear the names

00:05:50.080 --> 00:05:50.940
of General Feng

00:05:51.480 --> 00:05:52.810
and your entire family.

00:05:53.520 --> 00:05:53.980
Li Ling.

00:06:04.720 --> 00:06:06.180
The criminal Feng Jianye.

00:06:06.360 --> 00:06:07.480
Defied imperial orders

00:06:07.480 --> 00:06:08.880
and resisted passively.

00:06:08.880 --> 00:06:10.320
Colluded with the enemy and betrayed the country.

00:06:10.320 --> 00:06:12.780
Attempted to obstruct the imperial mission

00:06:12.880 --> 00:06:14.760
and plotted to overthrow the state.

00:06:14.760 --> 00:06:15.960
He must be eliminated

00:06:16.560 --> 00:06:17.800
without mercy.

00:06:22.760 --> 00:06:23.690
That's not true.

00:06:23.800 --> 00:06:26.400
The general and I fought desperately on the battlefield.

00:06:26.400 --> 00:06:28.560
How could he possibly betray his country?

00:06:28.560 --> 00:06:29.040
Sir.

00:06:29.520 --> 00:06:30.800
I am the general's deputy commander.

00:06:30.800 --> 00:06:32.530
We have been here all this time.

00:06:32.680 --> 00:06:33.440
I know the truth.

00:06:33.440 --> 00:06:34.680
The truth is not like this.

00:06:34.680 --> 00:06:35.140
Li Ling.

00:06:35.760 --> 00:06:37.120
Silence! Don't say another word.

00:06:37.120 --> 00:06:37.650
General.

00:06:37.840 --> 00:06:38.480
Stop talking.

00:06:38.480 --> 00:06:39.210
How dare you!

00:06:39.880 --> 00:06:41.480
You're just a minor officer.

00:06:41.840 --> 00:06:43.900
How dare you defy the Emperor's will!

00:06:45.880 --> 00:06:47.600
And you, Feng Jianye.

00:06:48.240 --> 00:06:50.760
Allowing your subordinate to disobey imperial orders.

00:06:50.760 --> 00:06:53.020
Do you know what punishment you deserve?

00:06:53.880 --> 00:06:55.140
Please calm down, sir.

00:06:55.159 --> 00:06:57.200
A soldier's duty is to obey orders.

00:06:57.520 --> 00:07:00.720
Both punishment and favor come from His Majesty's grace.

00:07:01.960 --> 00:07:04.420
I, Feng Jianye, accept the imperial decree.

00:07:04.600 --> 00:07:05.760
But I also believe...

00:07:05.760 --> 00:07:06.640
Heaven's principles are clear.

00:07:06.640 --> 00:07:07.700
Right and wrong...

00:07:07.880 --> 00:07:09.520
His Majesty will be just.

00:07:10.680 --> 00:07:11.210
General.

00:07:11.560 --> 00:07:12.040
Leave.

00:07:12.440 --> 00:07:13.370
That's an order.

00:07:14.680 --> 00:07:15.000
General.

00:07:15.000 --> 00:07:15.440
Get up.

00:07:15.520 --> 00:07:16.050
Let's go.

00:07:16.440 --> 00:07:17.040
General.

00:07:20.920 --> 00:07:21.250
Move.

00:07:44.760 --> 00:07:45.220
Father,

00:07:45.400 --> 00:07:46.130
don't worry.

00:07:46.320 --> 00:07:47.760
When Chang'an is liberated,

00:07:47.760 --> 00:07:49.820
I will surely engrave your name on it.

00:08:11.160 --> 00:08:12.760
Master Chen, please have a look.

00:08:12.760 --> 00:08:15.880
This is Feng Jianye's priceless treasure,

00:08:16.120 --> 00:08:17.250
the Yu Linxun sword.

00:08:23.880 --> 00:08:26.610
Indeed, it's a blade sharp enough to split a hair.

00:08:27.240 --> 00:08:27.600
Sir,

00:08:27.880 --> 00:08:29.610
An Lushan's envoy has arrived.

00:08:32.080 --> 00:08:33.760
This great victory at Tongguan Pass

00:08:33.760 --> 00:08:36.039
is all thanks to General Chen's brilliant strategy.

00:08:36.039 --> 00:08:38.760
His Majesty praises you as Great Yan's fortunate general.

00:08:38.760 --> 00:08:41.159
And the Night Firefly Map in your possession

00:08:41.159 --> 00:08:42.679
was the key to our victory.

00:08:43.080 --> 00:08:45.080
To be recognized by Emperor Xiongwu

00:08:45.200 --> 00:08:46.880
is my great fortune.

00:08:47.640 --> 00:08:49.700
For the grand ambitions of Great Yan,

00:08:49.880 --> 00:08:51.440
I am willing to sacrifice everything,

00:08:51.440 --> 00:08:52.640
whatever it takes.

00:08:54.880 --> 00:08:55.440
Good.

00:08:55.520 --> 00:08:56.080
Good.

00:08:58.320 --> 00:09:00.240
What about Feng Jianye?

00:09:01.120 --> 00:09:02.600
That stubborn fellow.

00:09:03.080 --> 00:09:05.200
I tried to persuade him for hours,

00:09:05.360 --> 00:09:07.620
but he absolutely refuses to surrender.

00:09:08.240 --> 00:09:09.800
If he cannot serve us,

00:09:10.560 --> 00:09:13.200
then we must eliminate any future threat.

00:09:14.880 --> 00:09:16.080
Rest assured, Envoy.

00:09:16.640 --> 00:09:18.040
I've made arrangements.

00:09:18.680 --> 00:09:22.240
Today, Feng Jianye will attempt to escape prison and fail,

00:09:22.640 --> 00:09:24.320
dying under a hail of blades.

00:09:30.520 --> 00:09:31.440
General Feng,

00:09:31.560 --> 00:09:32.290
we're sorry,

00:09:32.640 --> 00:09:34.440
but we're here to end your life.

00:09:42.600 --> 00:09:43.280
General!

00:09:59.440 --> 00:09:59.970
General.

00:10:01.280 --> 00:10:03.360
Chen Jingbian, you treacherous dog!

00:10:04.200 --> 00:10:05.060
Chen Jingbian.

00:10:06.760 --> 00:10:08.360
We can't return to Chang'an anymore.

00:10:08.360 --> 00:10:09.690
We can go to Western Shu.

00:10:09.760 --> 00:10:11.360
We'll find the Emperor there

00:10:11.520 --> 00:10:12.980
and seek justice from him.

00:10:13.920 --> 00:10:15.120
Listen to me.

00:10:16.000 --> 00:10:17.330
My life doesn't matter,

00:10:18.240 --> 00:10:20.240
but the foundation of our great Tang

00:10:20.560 --> 00:10:22.960
must never fall into enemy hands.

00:10:23.920 --> 00:10:26.440
Now the Emperor has fled west,

00:10:27.080 --> 00:10:29.410
Chen Jingbian has surrendered Chang'an,

00:10:29.720 --> 00:10:31.880
and half of our Tang territory

00:10:32.720 --> 00:10:34.520
has already fallen apart.

00:10:36.240 --> 00:10:38.120
As long as the traitors remain,

00:10:38.760 --> 00:10:40.480
the war will continue.

00:10:40.840 --> 00:10:42.560
Weapons will clash everywhere,

00:10:42.560 --> 00:10:43.960
people will suffer,

00:10:44.760 --> 00:10:47.520
and civilians will have no way to survive.

00:10:47.640 --> 00:10:48.200
General,

00:10:49.040 --> 00:10:50.440
we need to heal you first.

00:10:51.680 --> 00:10:53.040
I've long known

00:10:54.000 --> 00:10:55.930
that Chen Jingbian, that villain,

00:10:56.480 --> 00:10:58.320
would become a great threat.

00:10:59.240 --> 00:10:59.880
Li Ling.

00:11:01.000 --> 00:11:02.560
You must find a way

00:11:03.040 --> 00:11:05.320
to get the Night Firefly Map from him.

00:11:05.320 --> 00:11:05.850
General!

00:11:06.160 --> 00:11:08.480
It's crucial

00:11:08.480 --> 00:11:10.210
for our Tang's future victory.

00:11:10.480 --> 00:11:11.010
General,

00:11:14.360 --> 00:11:15.320
it's too late.

00:11:16.160 --> 00:11:18.080
I don't have much time left.

00:11:18.080 --> 00:11:19.210
No, that's not true.

00:11:21.640 --> 00:11:22.880
Do you remember

00:11:24.200 --> 00:11:26.360
what I told you that day

00:11:27.480 --> 00:11:29.410
when you touched the jade carving?

00:11:30.280 --> 00:11:32.720
The person you become

00:11:33.800 --> 00:11:36.080
is not determined by your birth,

00:11:37.000 --> 00:11:38.960
but is held

00:11:40.000 --> 00:11:41.840
in your own hands.

00:11:42.600 --> 00:11:43.260
General...

00:11:44.080 --> 00:11:45.760
You... use your hands

00:11:46.920 --> 00:11:49.560
to build your own achievements.

00:11:50.800 --> 00:11:52.720
You are the best soldier

00:11:54.040 --> 00:11:55.360
I've ever trained.

00:12:02.360 --> 00:12:03.280
General!

00:12:08.200 --> 00:12:12.080
Take my head to Chen Jingbian.

00:12:12.560 --> 00:12:15.280
He's naturally suspicious.

00:12:16.120 --> 00:12:16.960
Only this way

00:12:17.080 --> 00:12:21.160
can you infiltrate and get the map.

00:12:22.040 --> 00:12:22.500
I won't.

00:12:22.920 --> 00:12:23.380
I can't.

00:12:23.920 --> 00:12:24.880
Do it.

00:12:25.880 --> 00:12:26.960
Li Ling,

00:12:27.600 --> 00:12:30.280
do it now!

00:12:30.480 --> 00:12:30.840
No!

00:12:31.760 --> 00:12:35.600
This is a military order!

00:12:35.960 --> 00:12:39.920
Do it now!

